What happened at Grossmont Hospital (@sharphealthcare) was just ridiculous. First off, the good news is that I dont have cancer in my brain. Yay!

Second, I came into contact with Dr. Anthony Mells. He doesnt believe in pain meds for 9 out of 10 pain for a cancer patient. 1/?

@nofish_nonuts 2 cups sugar, 4 tbsp of maple syrup or honey, pinch of salt, 3 tbsp of cinnamon, and 2 cups walnuts. Cook everything except the walnuts until hard crack/ball stage. Add 3 tbsp of butter. Cook until mixed. Add walnuts for 2-3 minutes. Pour out on greased cookie sheet. Cool. Eat!!
